      • test_simpleFixPoint

        public void test_simpleFixPoint()
                         throws Exception
        Example using only RuleRdfs11 that requires multiple rounds to compute the fix point closure of a simple data set. This example is based on closure of the class hierarchy. Given 
         a sco b
 b sco c
 c sco d
        round 1 adds 
         a sco c
 b sco d
        round 2 adds 
         a sco d
        and that is the fixed point.
        Throws:
        Exception
